See also:   http://www.iram.fr/IRAMFR/GILDAS/


grab the two tar balls, in my case
   gildas-doc-dec07a.tar.gz 
   gildas-src-dec07a.tar.gz


tar zxf gildas-src-dec07a.tar.gz 
cd gildas-src-dec07a
astroload intel			need intel compiler
sh				(bash doesn't inherit the shell??)
source admin/gildas-env.sh 
make
make install

